  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if using 20 mL B.Braun syringes to inflate LMAs and
      allowing them to recoil will put the pressure of the LMA cuff within the safety range. It
      will also determine if remaining within this safety range has an effect on complications
      after surgery..
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
